high_descs: Turn around, walk to the kitchen island
Grab the spatula on the island
Turn right, and turn left, walk to the sink
Put the spatula in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the spatula, turn off the faucet, take the spatula
Open the first drawer from the top, put the spatula in, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Wash the spatula, put it in the first drawer

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the island
Pick up the spatula from the island.
Walk around the island to the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around to face the stove.
Put the spatula in the drawer to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed spatula in the drawer next to the stove.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the end of the island and turn left to face it.
Take the spatula on the counter.
Turn right and then left going around the island and then left to face the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink and turn the water on. Turn off the water and take the spatula back out.
Turn left then right to face the stove and then look down below.
Pull out the first drawer next to the stove and put the spatula in the front below the fork and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To clean the spatula to put it in the drawer.
